sequenceDiagram
    participant Person as "Student"
    participant Front as "Browser"
    participant Back as "PHP Backend"
    participant DB as "MySQL"

    Person->>Front: Select & upload file
    Front->>Back: POST /index.php?route=upload
    Back->>Back: validate file type & size
    Back->>DB: INSERT INTO files
    DB->>Back: file_id
    Back->>Front: upload success
    Front->>Person: File uploaded message